# and ftp://maia.usno.navy.mil/ser7/tai-utc.dat
#
# To do things a little more accurately, I assembled the following from
# the above sources:
#
#  MJD   drift   step
# 41317        0  -0.1077580
# 39887 -300e-10   0.1
